            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="p2">每日你點擊無數次連結，每一個連結背後連到不同互聯網內容，但世界上透過網頁入侵電腦、手機的陷阱多如星屑，稍一不慎你很容易會隨時跌入黑客、騙徒陷阱，信用卡、帳户資料隨時被盜。被黑客竊取 Facebook、WhatsApp 帳户的個人、商户要取回帳户，是非常麻煩的一件事，信用卡被盜刷更是難於追討。如何可以得到更周全的保護，上網可以更加安心？除了 VPN 之外，你還需要一個<a href="https://surfshark.com/zh-hk/deal/one?coupon=onedeal&amp;transaction_id=102a2a6bf03ff8881c18e56eb4f767&amp;offer_id=87&amp;affiliate_id=4476&amp;source=&amp;aff_sub=&amp;utm_source=Affiliates&amp;utm_medium=4476&amp;utm_campaign=affiliate&amp;recurring_goal_id=76">周全的網絡安全服務</a>。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1195608 aligncenter" src="https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/bundle-surfshark-one-woman-box@2x-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/bundle-surfshark-one-woman-box@2x-580x580.jpg 580w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/bundle-surfshark-one-woman-box@2x-900x900.jpg 900w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/bundle-surfshark-one-woman-box@2x-120x120.jpg 120w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/bundle-surfshark-one-woman-box@2x-768x768.jpg 768w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/bundle-surfshark-one-woman-box@2x-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/bundle-surfshark-one-woman-box@2x-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2 class="p2">避開有害軟件（Malware）入侵電腦、網路</h2><p class="p2">VPN 服務可以協助你避開黑客、騙徒的陷阱。目前最常令用户遭受損失的是網路上流傳的有害軟件（Malware）。有害軟件包括了電腦／手機病毒、蠕蟲、木馬、勒索軟件、廣告軟件等。這些有害軟件可在你的內部網絡上散佈更多間諜軟件、勒索軟件，更會消耗公司網絡的頻寬，更甚者會刪除公司網絡上電腦的檔案，為公司網絡打開大門，給黑客隨意入侵。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/scam-lottery.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1194886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/scam-lottery-694x396.png" alt="" width="694" height="396" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/scam-lottery-694x396.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/scam-lottery-1280x731.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/scam-lottery-768x439.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/scam-lottery-1536x877.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/scam-lottery.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p2">最常避免有害軟件的方法，就是在電腦安裝防毒軟件，隨時用 Windows Update、Mac 系統更新功能更新你的電腦堵塞網絡漏洞，不要隨便打開不明人士傳送給你的連結、文件，以至圖片，也不要實行不知名網站提供的檔案。有時電郵模仿大企業官方格式，需要你開啟檔案，不僅開啟就可能會中招。</p><p class="p2">你還可利用 VPN 協助你避開有害軟件。<a href="https://surfshark.com/zh-hk/deal/one?coupon=onedeal&amp;transaction_id=102a2a6bf03ff8881c18e56eb4f767&amp;offer_id=87&amp;affiliate_id=4476&amp;source=&amp;aff_sub=&amp;utm_source=Affiliates&amp;utm_medium=4476&amp;utm_campaign=affiliate&amp;recurring_goal_id=76">Surfshark CleanWeb Adblock VPN</a> 就可為你隔絕網路上的有害軟件、讓你避免點擊入有害的連結後中招。萬一你點擊了這些連結，VPN 會向你作出提示連結可能有安全風險，讓用户再三確認，可避免很多一 click 即中招的情況。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cybercrime-statistics-stats-graph.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1194885" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cybercrime-statistics-stats-graph-694x396.png" alt="" width="694" height="396" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cybercrime-statistics-stats-graph-694x396.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cybercrime-statistics-stats-graph-1280x731.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cybercrime-statistics-stats-graph-768x439.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cybercrime-statistics-stats-graph-1536x877.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Cybercrime-statistics-stats-graph.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 class="p2">避開釣魚攻擊洩漏你的信用卡、帳户資料</h2><p class="p2">釣魚攻擊是一個用户很易中招，洩漏信用卡、銀行帳户資料的渠道。不法份子透過一個設計與銀行、信用卡網站非常類似的網站介面，並以不同方式誘騙用户輸入個人資料。萬一用户輸入了自己的個人資料，資料會馬上被黑客獲取，並進行盜用、非法活動。</p><p class="p2">要避免受到釣魚攻擊，最好的方法就是自己上網時小心留意，不要隨便在電郵提供的網址中登入自己的帳户。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/data-breach-alert-computer-unlocked-steal.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1194884" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/data-breach-alert-computer-unlocked-steal-694x396.png" alt="" width="694" height="396" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/data-breach-alert-computer-unlocked-steal-694x396.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/data-breach-alert-computer-unlocked-steal-1280x730.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/data-breach-alert-computer-unlocked-steal-768x438.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/data-breach-alert-computer-unlocked-steal-1536x876.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/data-breach-alert-computer-unlocked-steal.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p2"><a href="https://surfshark.com/zh-hk/deal/one?coupon=onedeal&amp;transaction_id=102a2a6bf03ff8881c18e56eb4f767&amp;offer_id=87&amp;affiliate_id=4476&amp;source=&amp;aff_sub=&amp;utm_source=Affiliates&amp;utm_medium=4476&amp;utm_campaign=affiliate&amp;recurring_goal_id=76">Surfshark CleanWeb</a> 就可協助你阻擋網路上的釣魚攻擊。此功能結合 Adblock 可阻擋網路上已被標籤為釣魚攻擊的網站、連結，讓用户遠離釣魚攻擊的威脅。</p><h2 class="p2">避免企業伺服器「注入攻擊」</h2><p class="p2">「注入攻擊」是企業伺服器最經常面對的網路安全風險之一。黑客透過 SQL 隱碼 (SQL injection) 攻擊，將有害程式碼注入企業伺服器的資料庫中，可引致資料庫數據面臨被刪除、更改、洩漏的危機。至於另一種更危險的攻擊方式叫「跨網站指令碼」（Cross-site scripting），黑客會將有害程式碼注入企業網站的程式碼中，其他使用者在觀看網頁時便會受到影響，這對企業形象帶來不可估計的破壞。</p><p class="p2">很多時企業即使被黑客入侵，除非受到重大安全影響，否則也不會向用户通報，多數都暪天過海，最終用户會承擔帳户資料被盜風險。雖然 VPN 服務並不能防護，但 Surfshark 用户可同時使用該公司提供的 <a href="https://surfshark.com/zh-hk/deal/one?coupon=onedeal&amp;transaction_id=102a2a6bf03ff8881c18e56eb4f767&amp;offer_id=87&amp;affiliate_id=4476&amp;source=&amp;aff_sub=&amp;utm_source=Affiliates&amp;utm_medium=4476&amp;utm_campaign=affiliate&amp;recurring_goal_id=76">Surfshark Alert</a>，你存放於企業伺服器的帳户資料，即使被黑客盜取，<a href="https://surfshark.com/zh-hk/deal/one?coupon=onedeal&amp;transaction_id=102a2a6bf03ff8881c18e56eb4f767&amp;offer_id=87&amp;affiliate_id=4476&amp;source=&amp;aff_sub=&amp;utm_source=Affiliates&amp;utm_medium=4476&amp;utm_campaign=affiliate&amp;recurring_goal_id=76">Surfshark Alert</a> 可感應到這類意外，當你的帳户資料出現於市面上黑客販售的數據庫中，可即時向你通報，讓你及早實行對應措施，包括更改密碼、刪除帳户等。</p><h2 class="p2">DNS 快取污染</h2><p class="p2">用户連接網絡服務，其實背後都要靠一個「DNS」伺服器，將網址的文字，轉化成為連接到企業伺服器的網址。如果這個 DNS 快取受到污染，你將不能連到企業官方網站，反而會連到黑客所操蹤的網站。作為一個小用户，你可以使用 VPN 服務來檢測 DNS 快取污染的發生，避免落入黑客的圈套。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1195605 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-ads-cleanweb-block-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-ads-cleanweb-block-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-ads-cleanweb-block-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-ads-cleanweb-block-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-ads-cleanweb-block-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-ads-cleanweb-block-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-ads-cleanweb-block.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2 class="p2">要安全防護，避免不同種類的入侵</h2><p class="p2">VPN 可以為你提供網路連線安全保障，上網數據不受黑客竊聽。而為了避免其他網絡陷阱，用户可留意 <a href="https://surfshark.com/zh-hk/deal/one?coupon=onedeal&amp;transaction_id=102a2a6bf03ff8881c18e56eb4f767&amp;offer_id=87&amp;affiliate_id=4476&amp;source=&amp;aff_sub=&amp;utm_source=Affiliates&amp;utm_medium=4476&amp;utm_campaign=affiliate&amp;recurring_goal_id=76">Surfshark One</a> 最周全的網絡安全服務。此服務包括有 Surfshark VPN、Surfshark Antivirus 防毒軟件、Surfshark Search 提供安全搜尋結果、Surfshark Alert 在你的帳户資料萬一在黑客市場流通都可馬上向你通報。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1195606 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unlimited-devices-phone-interface-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unlimited-devices-phone-interface-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unlimited-devices-phone-interface-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unlimited-devices-phone-interface-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unlimited-devices-phone-interface-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unlimited-devices-phone-interface-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unlimited-devices-phone-interface.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2 class="p2">unwire 讀者優惠</h2><p class="p2">現在只要通過這條 <a href="https://surfshark.com/zh-hk/deal/one?coupon=onedeal&amp;transaction_id=102a2a6bf03ff8881c18e56eb4f767&amp;offer_id=87&amp;affiliate_id=4476&amp;source=&amp;aff_sub=&amp;utm_source=Affiliates&amp;utm_medium=4476&amp;utm_campaign=affiliate&amp;recurring_goal_id=76">Surfshark One 連結</a>進入官方網站，訂閲兩年就可即時享有 84% 優惠 + 2 個月免費，只需要 HK$23.02 一個月，就可以獲取上述提到的 Surfshark One 安全服務套餐。另外也可以選擇訂閲一年，優惠則是 77%。限時優惠，讀者們不要錯過。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1195607 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-blocked-access-hold-694x396.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="396" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-blocked-access-hold-694x396.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-blocked-access-hold-1280x731.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-blocked-access-hold-768x439.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/phone-blocked-access-hold-1536x877.jpg 1536w